quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  20,83,"(Ke kaloku ukufika kukaMûsâ kwintaba yeSinayi ebaleka eshiya abantu bakubo nomntakwabo uHârûn, uAllâh Wathi): “Yintoni na ekwenze ukuba ungxame ukumka kubantu bakuni wena Mûsâ?”"
  20,84,"Wathi yena: “Basondele kumzila weenyawo zam: Ke mna ndiye ndabalekela kuWe, Wena Nkosi yam, ukuze Wena Ukholiseke (ndim).”"
  20,85,"UAllâh Wathi: “Kodwa inene, Sibavavanyile abantu bakuni emva (kokumka) kwakho, ke kaloku uSâmirî ubakhokelele ekulahlekeni"
  20,86,"Wabuyela ke uMûsâ kubantu bakubo, enomsindo, ekhathazekile. Wathi: “Hini na bantu bakuthi, ingaba iNkosi yenu Ayinenzelanga isithembiso esilungileyo na? Ingaba ke ngoku ixesha (lokuzalisekiswa kwaso) besele likude kangako na kuni, okanye niye nanqwenela ukuba ingqumbo ka-Allâh ihle phezu kwenu, kangokuba nide naphule isithembiso senu (sokundithobela) mna?”"
  20,87,"Bathi bona: “Asisaphulanga isithembiso sethu kuwe, kodwa siye senzelwa ubunzima kukuthwaliswa imithwalo yezihombiso zabantu (bakwaFir’awn), siye sazijulela emlilweni waza ngolo hlobo noSâmirî1 wazijula ke"
  20,88,"Keyenauyewakhuphakuzoitholeebelinesandiesigxwalayo”, baza bathi: “Lo nguthixo wenu onguthixo kaMûsâ, kodwa yena (uMûsâ) ulibele (akabuyi).”"
  20,89,"Babengaboni na bona ukuba lalingakwazi kubuyisa nto entethweni (lalingaphenduli), kwanokuba lalingenabo nabungozi lingenalo nancedo kubo"
  20,90,"NoHârûn wayesele ebaxelele ngaphambili (wathi): “Hini na bantu bakuthi, niyalingwa ngalo (ithole), kananjalo iNkosi yenu nguSozinceba, ngoko ke landelani mna nithobele umyalelo wam.”"
  20,91,"Bathi bona: “Asisokuze siyeke ukuzinikela kulo (eli thole) ade uMûsâ abuye eze kuthi.”"
  20,92,"UMûsâ wathi: “Hini na Hârûn, yintoni na ekuthinteleyo ngelixa ububabona bephambuka"
  20,93,Ekundilandeleni? Ingaba nawe akuwuthobelanga na umyalelo wam?”
  20,94,"(UHârûn) wathi: “Hini na mntwana kamama, musa ukunditsala ngeendevu zam okanye ngentloko yam. Inene mna ndiye ndoyikisela ukuba hleze uthi wena (kum), wena udale iyantlukwano phakathi kwaBantwana bakwaSirayeli, awukhanga uligcine ilizwi lam. ‘”"
  20,95,"(UMûsâ) wathi: “Kuye kwathini kuwe wena Sâmirî?”"
  20,96,"Wathi yena, “Ndiye ndabona oko mna bebengakuboni bona, ndaza ndakha isandla esigcweleyo (sothuli) kumzila weenyawo zesiThunywa2 ndaza ndasijula walukuhleka kanjalo ke umphefumlo wam.”"
  20,97,"(UMûsâ) wathi: “Hamba umke. Inene isohlwayo sakho kulo mhlaba siya kuba kukuba wena uthi: “Ungandichukumisi”3 kananjalo, inene wena unesithembiso (soBomi oBuzayo) ongayi kusilela ukusigcina. Khawujonge ‘kuthixo’ wakho lowo ubukade uzinikele kuye. Siya kumtshisa Size Simvuthelele (eluthuthu) elwandle ngesithonga"
  20,98,"UThixo wakho nguAllâh kuphela, akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe. Yena ke (uAllâh) Ugubungele zonke izinto ngolwazi.”"
  20,99,"Ngolo hlobo ke wena (Muhammad), Siyakubalisela kwiindaba zoko kwaqhubekayo ngaphambili. Kananjalo wena Sikunikile inkumbuzo (i’Kur’ân) evela kuThi"
  20,100,"Lowo uyitshikilelayo (le ‘Kur’ân), inene yena ngoMhla woVuko uya kuthwala umthwalo (omkhulu wezono)"
  20,101,"Baya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade, awumbi ngako umthwalo wabo ngoMhla woVuko"
  20,102,"NgeMini iXilongo liya kuvuthelwa: ngaloo Mini, Siya kubaqokelela abenzi bobubi betsho ngamehlo azuba"
  20,103,"Baya kuthetha ngamazwi aphantsi omnye komnye (besithi): “Anihlelanga ngaphezulu kuneshumi leentsuku (emhlabeni).”"
  20,104,"Sikwazi kakuhle abaza kukuthetha, xa oyena unolwazi kubo aya kuthi: “Anihlelanga ngaphezulu kunosuku olunye!”"
  20,105,"Ke kaloku bakubuza ngeentaba: Yithi, “INkosi yam Iza kuziqhushumbisa, Izichithe zibe ngamasuntswana othuli"
  20,106,Ize Izishiye zilele tyaba (zingamathafa)
  20,107,“Akuyi kubona nto igoso apho okanye egobileyo.”
  20,108,"Ngayo loo Mini abantu baya kulandela ngqongqo (ilizwi) lomkhwazi ka-Allâh, akukho bugoso-goso baya kuMbonisa bona. Kananjalo zonke (izandi) zamazwi ziya kuthobeka phambi koSolubabalo (uAllâh), yaye akukho nto uya kuyiva ngaphandle kwamazwi aphantsi ezingqi zeenyawo zabo"
  20,109,"Ngayo loo Mini akukho ntethelelo iya kunceda, ngaphandle kweyalowo uSolubabalo (uAllâh) Amnike imvume nelizwi lakhe liya kwamkeleka kuYe"
  20,110,"Yena (uAllâh) Uyakwazi okwenzekayo kuzo (izidalwa zaKhe) kweli hlabathi, noko kuza kwenzeka (kwilixa elisezayo) kodwa zona angekhe zibe nako ukuqulatha olo lwazi lwaKhe"